==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Withdrawing-room
<hw>With*draw"ing-room`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Withdraw</er>, and cf. <er>Drawing-room</er>.]</ety> <def>A room for
retirement from another room, as from a dining room; a
drawing-room.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A door in the middle leading to a parlor and
<qex>withdrawing-room</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Sir W. Scott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Withdrawment</ent>⟦br⟧
